{"tid":700015,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"劉曉波銅像揭幕 支聯會發起聯署︰釋放劉霞","createTime":"2018-06-13T03:59:44.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-13T04:22:45.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"56012843e1f32b72ed0c55c14eec45d5d4b39708","tid":700015,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T03:59:44.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419387\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419387&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=46e28054\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180613%2F20419387&h=7fcaa2a5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180613/20419387</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月13日 <br />\n<br />\n劉曉波銅像揭幕<br />\n支聯會發起聯署︰釋放劉霞<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諾貝爾和平獎得主劉曉波因參與起草《零八憲章》被控以「煽動顛覆國家政權罪」判處有期徒刑11年。去年確診末期肝癌同逝世，但其妻劉霞一直被軟禁在家。有熱心市民自費訂製劉曉波銅像，即日起至下月13日(劉曉波逝世一周年當日)，於銅鑼灣時代廣場對出空地展示供市民悼念憑弔，支聯會同時發起網上聯署，促中國國家主席習近平釋放劉霞。<br />\n<br />\n支聯會主席何俊仁昨日出席銅像揭幕儀式，呼籲外界關注劉曉波遺孀劉霞情況，並發起「釋放劉霞」全球聯署行動，市民可於7月11日或之前登入 <a href=\"https://form.jotform.me/81611618372455參與網上聯署，呼籲世界各地民眾致函中國國家主席習近平要求釋放劉霞，立即停止一切對劉霞的騷擾、監控和軟禁，確保劉霞基本權利，包括於國內外行動自由，並按照劉霞意願離開中國。支聯會會在劉曉波忌辰當日，將信件及聯署名單一併郵寄予習近平。\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fform.jotform.me%2F81611618372455%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%EF%BC%8C%E5%91%BC%E7%B1%B2%E4%B8%96%E7%95%8C%E5%90%84%E5%9C%B0%E6%B0%91%E7%9C%BE%E8%87%B4%E5%87%BD%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%B6%E4%B8%BB%E5%B8%AD%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E8%A6%81%E6%B1%82%E9%87%8B%E6%94%BE%E5%8A%89%E9%9C%9E%EF%BC%8C%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%B3%E5%81%9C%E6%AD%A2%E4%B8%80%E5%88%87%E5%B0%8D%E5%8A%89%E9%9C%9E%E7%9A%84%E9%A8%B7%E6%93%BE%E3%80%81%E7%9B%A3%E6%8E%A7%E5%92%8C%E8%BB%9F%E7%A6%81%EF%BC%8C%E7%A2%BA%E4%BF%9D%E5%8A%89%E9%9C%9E%E5%9F%BA%E6%9C%AC%E6%AC%8A%E5%88%A9%EF%BC%8C%E5%8C%85%E6%8B%AC%E6%96%BC%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E5%A4%96%E8%A1%8C%E5%8B%95%E8%87%AA%E7%94%B1%EF%BC%8C%E4%B8%A6%E6%8C%89%E7%85%A7%E5%8A%89%E9%9C%9E%E6%84%8F%E9%A1%98%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E3%80%82%E6%94%AF%E8%81%AF%E6%9C%83%E6%9C%83%E5%9C%A8%E5%8A%89%E6%9B%89%E6%B3%A2%E5%BF%8C%E8%BE%B0%E7%95%B6%E6%97%A5%EF%BC%8C%E5%B0%87%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B6%E5%8F%8A%E8%81%AF%E7%BD%B2%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE%E4%B8%80%E4%BD%B5%E9%83%B5%E5%AF%84%E4%BA%88%E7%BF%92%E8%BF%91%E5%B9%B3%E3%80%82&d=8RTelL83%2BhILtVv%2FCeYAPrr9WXPazFMcT8p8rn878U0%3D&h=e52441e8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://form.jotform.me/81611618372455參與網上聯署，呼籲世界各地民眾致函中國國家主席習近平要求釋放劉霞，立即停止一切對劉霞的騷擾、監控和軟禁，確保劉霞基本權利，包括於國內外行動自由，並按照劉霞意願離開中國。支聯會會在劉曉波忌辰當日，將信件及聯署名單一併郵寄予習近平。</a>  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n西環集中營：7.1遊行前　林鄭拆彈省靚政績 (季陶)<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n爆相爆片"},{"pid":"8047a3dd1abf00fab19c5f465b7dd380c909a204","tid":700015,"uid":158074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"新方法 cap 水"},{"pid":"d3a313e19617254b90ebe2ddd388e57bc903fe22","tid":700015,"uid":127177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8047a3dd1abf00fab19c5f465b7dd380c909a204","tid":700015,"uid":158074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:02:48.000Z","msg":"新方法 cap 水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-13T04:22:45.000Z","msg":"仲搭棚?仲有人肯制?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}